title: Harvick dominates in must-win race to advance in Chase
text:
> North Carolina Harvick dominates in must-win race to advance in Chase Kevin Harvick drives his car during the NASCAR Sprint Cup series auto race, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, at Dover International Speedway in Dover, Del.
